The app aims to facilitate setting up the children\'s dose, which is generally directed for dear pharmacists and doctors colleagues. Also with all respect, it is directed to my colleagues at the clinic of UNRWA in particular. Most information in this app has references due to booklets that are: STG ( Standard Treatment Guidelines) , technical instructions on the management of 10 most common health conditions encountered in underway healthcare facilities and the medical website (Medscape). Development Reem Al-Sibakhi Disclaimer " calculations must be re-checked and should not be used alone to guide patient care , nor should they substitute for clinical judgment" Family Health in UNRWA health program Medscape
